    "severity": "Sev-2 (High)",
    "description": "Long Running Job Failure incident on the Inventory pipeline (RTL_INV_LRJF): suppliers EDI ASN ingestion fails on disk full.",
    "symptoms": "Vendor ASN ingestion DAG fails after 2h50m when the worker's local disk fills up during a large SFTP-to-Parquet conversion step.",
    "root_cause": "A single vendor (holiday collection supplier) sent an unusually large batch of ASN files (14GB vs typical 400MB) and the conversion task streams to local disk before uploading to MinIO, with no disk-space pre-check.",
    "business_impact": "Inbound shipment visibility lost for that vendor's holiday collection, delaying receiving dock scheduling.",
    "resolution": "Stream SFTP-to-Parquet conversion directly to MinIO instead of local disk; add a pre-flight disk-space check task."
  },
